{"tid":2428082,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"成功既關鍵，就係專注做好可控制既野","createTime":"2021-03-01T09:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T10:04:45.000Z","uid":123335,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4db72ef239977f1d02de52725e855d22fce7b04d","tid":2428082,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"不論股市，或係人生<br />\n專注你可以控制嘅嘢，先至係關鍵<br />\n<br />\n以投資股票為例，你可以控制啲咩？<br />\n可以控制到一定贏錢？ <br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">No ! </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不論是贏錢與否，你既預測是否準確<br />\n你都不能控制<br />\n<ins>你只能專注於：</ins><br />\n<strong>1）做好宏觀經濟分析，eg 要緊貼 Fomc 及債息走勢<br />\n2）做好功課分析個股基本面 &amp; 技術面 <br />\n3）注碼控制<br />\n4）制定交易策略</strong><br />\n<br />\n然後，你便需要運氣，<br />\n來達成成功 💪🏻<br />\n<br />\n雖然我並不想承認成功的背後需要運氣，<br />\n但這卻是事實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41782cdf4d4445c260752c15dec020b66156a2e","tid":2428082,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2536e051ed5bb372016b02ebff79796c274bb665","tid":2428082,"uid":375958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"real"},{"pid":"345d039112d086d180fd097c064a04b30b64dcec","tid":2428082,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"彪哥呢排出post好密喔"},{"pid":"e79971ea7f1fdeea2e272e7b415f3911b2f9f3ca","tid":2428082,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345d039112d086d180fd097c064a04b30b64dcec","tid":2428082,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"彪哥呢排出post好密喔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"突然對人生有感而發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aad3a561c745c825f0a04d93660dd4c075b3